Your safety is our #1 priority. Here's how you can enjoy Pi without a worry.

No Contact Pickup + Delivery: Our green tape system separates each customer while waiting for orders. For delivery, orders can be left at your doorstep. 

Our Safety Seal: Our freshness seal goes on every box. it ensures that no one has tampered with your food and must be ripped open by the customer. 

Online Ordering: We're encouraging online ordering to minimize the interaction between staff and customers. Place your order at pi-co.ca/order-online

Daily Deals: We've teamed up with our delivery partners to offer exclusive promotions.

We're Here: If you have any questions or concerns, please reach out. Our team is working continually to make this uneasy time a little easier. Stay well, everyone.

To Our Valued Guests:

The Firkin Group of Pubs places the health and well-being of our employees, our guests and our communities as a core value of our business.

In support of our local health authorities in the effort to combat the spread of COVID-19, we will be closing all of our locations as of March 16th, 2020.

Our friends at The Gull & Firkin are
Open for Pick-Up & Delivery on Uber Eats only.

Our friends at Firkin on Danforth are
Open for Pick-Up & Delivery on Uber Eats only.

We will be reopening when advised it is safe for us to do so.

In these turbulent and uncharted times, we wish you and your families to be safe and stay well.

We look forward to pouring you a pint soon.

Larry Isaacs
President, The Firkin Group of Pubs

name: Pi Co
Covid Banner:
Your safety is our #1 priority. Here's how you can enjoy Pi without a worry.

No Contact Pickup + Delivery: Our green tape system separates each customer while waiting for orders. For delivery, orders can be left at your doorstep. 

Our Safety Seal: Our freshness seal goes on every box. it ensures that no one has tampered with your food and must be ripped open by the customer. 

Online Ordering: We're encouraging online ordering to minimize the interaction between staff and customers. Place your order at pi-co.ca/order-online

Daily Deals: We've teamed up with our delivery partners to offer exclusive promotions.

We're Here: If you have any questions or concerns, please reach out. Our team is working continually to make this uneasy time a little easier. Stay well, everyone.

Covid Banner:
To Our Valued Guests:

The Firkin Group of Pubs places the health and well-being of our employees, our guests and our communities as a core value of our business.

In support of our local health authorities in the effort to combat the spread of COVID-19, we will be closing all of our locations as of March 16th, 2020.

Our friends at The Gull & Firkin are
Open for Pick-Up & Delivery on Uber Eats only.

Our friends at Firkin on Danforth are
Open for Pick-Up & Delivery on Uber Eats only.

We will be reopening when advised it is safe for us to do so.

In these turbulent and uncharted times, we wish you and your families to be safe and stay well.

We look forward to pouring you a pint soon.

Larry Isaacs
President, The Firkin Group of Pubs

To Our Valued Guests:

The Firkin Group of Pubs places the health and well-being of our employees, our guests and our communities as a core value of our business.

Open for Pick-Up & Delivery on Uber Eats only.

Our friends at Firkin on Danforth are
Open for Pick-Up & Delivery on Uber Eats only.

We will be reopening when advised it is safe for us to do so.

In these turbulent and uncharted times, we wish you and your families to be safe and stay well.

We look forward to pouring you a pint soon.

Larry Isaacs
President, The Firkin Group of Pubs
